Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:08.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Module 1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:16.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,What makes Hermes Agent fundamentally different
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:27.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,ChatGPT gives you answers. Hermes gets things done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:38.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,It lives in your terminal. Connected to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:48.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,It runs commands, writes files, fixes errors automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:58.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,Open source. MIT license. Built by Nous Research.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:08.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,20+ LLM providers. Zero lock-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:20.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,Persistent memory. Self-improving skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:32.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,70+ tools. Multi-platform. Cron jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:45.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,Runs 24/7 on a $5 VPS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:02:00.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,This isn't a chatbot. It's your autonomous agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:30.00,Cap,,0,0,0,,Let's get started with Module 1